    "description": "MakeMyTrip Hotels Advisory Limited invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Guest Relations Manager at our Delhi location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout MakeMyTrip Hotels Advisory Limited:\nMakeMyTrip Hotels Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage reservations and optimize room revenue through yield management\n• Prepare daily operating reports and present to management\n• Monitor F&B service quality and maintain hygiene standards\n• Train and supervise front-line staff on service standards\n• Develop and maintain relationships with corporate clients\n• Assist in menu planning, costing, and food festival coordination\n• Manage procurement of hotel supplies and control operating costs\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Customer Relations\n• Proficiency in Yield Management\n• Proficiency in Front Office\n• Proficiency in GDS Systems\n• Proficiency in MICE\n• Proficiency in Food Safety\n• Proficiency in PMS Systems\n• Proficiency in Barista Skills\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Delhi, Delhi, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with MakeMyTrip Hotels Advisory Limited!",
